beer.beer_description:
SAAZ / MOTUEKA / SIMCOE

This time our love of R&D sent us down the Thiol rabbit hole as far as we legally & logistically can here in Australia.


At its core this DIPA is uncomplicated, none of that Phancy stuff, just a solid mash addition of Saaz and a little dry-hop to make it pop.
beer.beer_style: IPA - Imperial / Double New England / Hazy
